7UAQ-qOd-Fc.title: 15 MIN Yoga For Flexibility | Stretch Class To Release Tight Hips, Legs, & Increase Mobility
7UAQ-qOd-Fc.description:
A 15 minute yoga for flexibility stretch class will guide you through a sequence of deep yoga postures that will release tight hips, sore legs, & increase mobility. Focusing on gently preparing the hips through various intensity building asanas to finish the class with the middle splits. This is the perfect Boho Beautiful yoga class for anyone looking to increase their lower body flexibility and master the middle splits. 

Remember, go slow, be gentle and patient with your body. Building flexibility takes time so do you best to incorporate these yoga poses as much as you can to your regular practice. 


Yoga Instructor- Juliana Spicoluk

ltE8w4SSDJs.title: Yin Yoga for Upper Body | Release ALL Stress & Tension In 30 Minutes
ltE8w4SSDJs.description:
This 30 minute upper body Yin Yoga class will provide immediate relief for your sore or painful upper back, neck, shoulders, arms, and chest. Through a series of mindfully deep muscle releasing asanas this Boho Beautiful Yoga sequence Mark Spicoluk will provide you the tools & space necessary to target all that is no longer serving you in order to first recognize it, then breathe through it, and finally... find your liberation.  

Yin Yoga is about breath. It's about following your breath to create the space necessary to ultimately reconnect to your inner stillness. Inside that stillness yin yoga allows you to cultivate peace with whatever is going on inside both your mind and body surrounding that stillness, in order to find acceptance, forgiveness, and then ultimately complete deliverance from it. 

So throughout this class, remember to use your breath as the string to guide you back to your deliberate attention and conscious awareness... for those are the gateway to all that you are looking for. 

So grab your mat, and some water, and don't forget to work hard and have fun. 

Yoga Instructor: Mark Spicoluk
Location: Costa Rica

RmRYbVyNLJY.title: We Got The Covid ugh 😑 | Back In Costa Rica Livestream 🇨🇷
RmRYbVyNLJY.description:
Today we launch our get back on your mat campaign, which we too are beginning as well!

THREE initiatives from our hearts to yours to help you get back to your intentions you set at the beginning of January:⁣⁣
⁣⁣
1. We revamped the entire 14 DAY FREE Yoga and Meditation Journey. FREE for all who want to experience a Boho Beautiful Program and all they have to offer!  
https://www.bohobeautiful.life/freeyoga
⁣⁣
2. Our entire store 30 % OFF SALE. Ascension, Transform,Retreat, Detoxify programs, all discounted at 30% for a limited time only. ⁣⁣
https://shop.bohobeautiful.life
⁣⁣
3. Our Boho Beautiful Official Annual Memberships are on sale at 30% OFF. ⁣⁣
https://www.bohobeautiful.tv
⁣⁣
The moments where we find the most growth in life is after we fall off, fall away, or get pushed down and have to find it in us to get back up. ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
So if you’ve lost touch with your intentions that you set at the beginning of the year, maybe ur coming back from a sickness or injury, or if you are simply finding it hard to keep yourself motivated…⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Then we hope that this little initiative will give you that gentle support to get back up! ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
This month, is your month…⁣⁣
To find space and time for yourself. ⁣⁣
Turn off all the noise. ⁣⁣
Take a deep breath. ⁣⁣

And get yourself back up on your mat. ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Sending you all of our love and light ❤️⁣⁣
⁣⁣
J&M

RFk9SDvhpHM.description:

A perfect deep stretch flexibility yoga session that doubles as an incredible thirty minute recovery practice too for your hamstrings, glutes, calves, and entire lower back as well. 

A yoga session designed for hikers, runners, and anyone who has been on their feet for way too many hours.  It's also great for anyone who has spent too much time sitting upright- which includes at a desk or anywhere that refuses to serve your body well. 

These days it's becoming a common professional understanding that 'sitting is the new smoking'.

Remember to listen to your body.  
Remember to breathe steadily & consciously as much as possible. 
And remember to relax and always have fun. 

... Namaste

X2OaMAUEPXM.title: Morning Guided Meditation | 10 Minutes To Execute The Perfect Day
X2OaMAUEPXM.description:
Try listening every morning to this ten minute guided meditation to set your mind and day up with a runway for perfect success, happiness, & focus. 

This 10 minute meditation will give you the space for mindfulness & mental clarity necessary to ground yourself perfectly in a clean start and a fresh slate, in order to create and access all that you need for a deep feeling of control and fulfillment. 

Taking the initiative every morning to find a quiet space to sit with yourself in stillness and meditate is one of the most simple and easy gifts that we can award to ourselves. This is because the space created each day only becomes stronger and more clear over time, and therefore more valuable for you to come back to yourself each time, strengthen your conscious focus, and then continue on with clarity and momentum into all that needs to be done in the day ahead. 

May you have the best day that you deserve. 

Love & Light....

seMW0kO-nNo.title: Yoga For Back Pain & Sciatica Relief | Heal, Strengthen, & Live A Pain Free Life
seMW0kO-nNo.description:
This 30 minute gentle yoga class will help fix back pain, relieve sciatic nerve discomfort, and release a sore or tight lower body. Then secondarily through a series of yoga asanas and exercises, the idea of this yoga class is not just to cure the pain but also build strength, mobility, and flexibility to help support and maintain a pain free life.  

This Boho Beautiful yoga for back pain relief consists of postures and movements that are part of Mark Spicoluk's personal recovery practice that he used to heal his sciatica pain and disk herniation. 

Remember, if you are healing and recovering from an injury please listen to your body and skip or modify any exercises or postures that do not feel right for you. And MAKE SURE to ask for guidance from your therapist or doctor before beginning any new exercise while healing an injury. 

Our FREE 14 Day Yoga Journey

KQfXOaLja5o.title: Gentle Evening Yoga | 20 Min Bedtime Yoga To Wind Down & Wash Away Stress
KQfXOaLja5o.description:
This 20 minute bedtime yoga to wind down is the evening yoga class to gently let go of all that no longer serves you. 
Through a series of asanas and mindful breathing we will journey inward to reconnect to the working of our own consciousness & the beating of our own heart, and remove ourselves from the memory and imprints of all that we experienced throughout the day.  

There is no greater tool that yoga to set yourself up for a perfect sleep and a wonderful beginning in the morning once again. 

Remember to drink a lot of water and when your mind wanders away always use the breath as the string to pull it back into focus. 
Also to breathe deep and have fun. 


Instructor- Mark Spicoluk 
Location- Rio Perdido, Costa Rica
https://www.rioperdido.com

nbFm_FRwS7o.title: How To Headstand & What To NEVER EVER Do! | Headstand For Beginners Masterclass
nbFm_FRwS7o.description:
Anyone can learn to do a headstand and this beginners step by step tutorial will show you exactly that. Salamba Sirsasana comes first through strength building, then balance, and always safety...  and no matter what level of yogi you are this Boho Beautiful yoga class can guide you to a perfect headstand execution. 

One of the main ideas of inversions like this is to experiment with your body and have fun. Yes, thats right... just like when we were all kids the idea is to find joy in both being upside and falling from time to time. Both are ideas for many years now most of us have been told we grow out of, however when we reintegrate them into our lives with joy, curiosity, and self love a whole new and familiar world opens up. 

So please 
Remember to listen to your body... 
DON'T push past your comfort zone.
AND make sure to put your weight on your arms NOT your actual head!
and most of all have fun. 
Because head-stands aren't just for the young, they are also for the young at heart!

Grab your mat, and don't forget to 
work hard & have fun. 

Yoga Instructor- Mark Spicoluk 

Location- Mystica, Costa Rica  http://www.mysticacostarica.com

zaWEtyB9Ggk.description:
After this 15 MIN beginner yoga workout don't forget to try out 1 device on Dashlane for free by going to http://www.dashlane.com/bohobeautiful & then if you wish to buy a premium plan receive 50% off with the code BohoBeautiful .

This short and effective yoga class is perfect for beginning your journey or starting to get back into shape again.  A well  rounded gentle and laid back full body workout for easing back onto your mat and laying the ground work for the journey to come. 

Remember this class is a guide, let it show you the path but make sure you listen to your body and work your way to what feels best. If a certain exercise doesn't feel right or is too much right now, do what you can but don't be afraid to sit it out and then pick up on the next exercise.  Then the next time you come to do this class you can do a little more, and the next time after that a little more. 
Everybody is at a different point on their journey. 
And where you are in this moment is perfect for you and only you!

Grab some water, and let's get on our mats!

This is a perfect deep stretch yoga class for after working out, standing, sitting, running, or walking more than your body is used to as it released tension, calms lactic acid release, detoxifies, and gives the attention a sore body craves.

khWzxsm0a8c.title: A Quick & Dirty New Year | New Free Program & Baby Imminent
khWzxsm0a8c.description:
Sign up for our new program here- https://www.bohobeautiful.life/freeyoga
Happy new year! Lets leave 2020 in the dirt and shine bright and vibrant together in 2021!

***

THIS VIDEO WAS SHOT IN GUIONES COSTA RICA

***

What Kind Of Classes Are A Part Of The 14 DAY Journey Ahead? 

Our goal with this program is to offer you a variation of many different styled of yoga and meditation classes.
 
YOGA
Each day a new type of 20-30 minute yoga class will be waiting for you ranging from:

- Feel Good Vinyasa Yoga Flows

- Yin Yoga Classes 

- Power Yoga Classes

- Yoga Workouts

- Gentle & Restorative Movement

SHdwAsUtRBg.title: 60 Minute Yoga Class | All Level Stress & Anxiety Release Live Yoga
SHdwAsUtRBg.description:
This relaxing 1 hour yoga class is an energy boosting all-levels yoga flow in support of raising awareness and funds for a wonderful organization Smile Train and their fourth annual Yoga For Smiles Campaign.
 
More 60, 45, and 30 minute  classes at: 
http://www.patreon.com/bohobeautiful 

We are hoping that you consider donating even the smallest amount in the spirit of Karma Yoga in exchange for participation. 

To learn more about Smile Train please visit: https://www.smiletrain.org 
To donate, please visit  https://www.smiletrain.org/yoga 

This Yoga class was shot on Monday June 29th The Sentinel in Kaslo BC, Canada 
http://sentinelbc.ca

Smile Train is an international children’s charity with a sustainable approach to a single solvable issue: cleft lip and palate. 

Smile Train empowers local medical professionals in more than 70+ countries with the resources that they need in order to provide comprehensive cleft care to children in their own communities. Since being founded in 1999, Smile Train has supported more than 1.5 million cleft surgeries.

Even as little as $5 can help a child receive 100% free cleft treatment, giving them not just a forever smile, but a second chance at life as well. 

See you on the mat!

#BohoBeautiful #Pilates #Workout

Boho Beautiful is Juliana Spicoluk and Mark Spicoluk

Smile Train is an international children’s charity with a sustainable approach to a single solvable issue: cleft lip and palate. 

Smile Train empowers local medical professionals in more than 70+ countries with the resources that they need in order to provide comprehensive cleft care to children in their own communities. Since being founded in 1999, Smile Train has supported more than 1.5 million cleft surgeries.

Even as little as $5 can help a child receive 100% free cleft treatment, giving them not just a forever smile, but a second chance at life as well.

BsKUBO_TPRk.description:
This 30 minute Yin Yoga practice is a perfect deep stretch class that not only releases sore and tired muscles but also excess emotion and negativity stored inside your body & mind. 

Through the yin practice of holding yoga asanas for 3 minutes each, this at home stretch will slowly allow your body to surrender to relaxation, mindfulness, and return back to deeply rich grounded presence.

Do not force anything. Just let it all come forward and find stillness inside of it.  That is where the great benefit will be found.

Roll out that mat and enjoy! XO

WHAT IS YIN YOGA?

Yin Yoga is a style of yoga practice that targets the connective tissues, such as the ligaments, bones, and even the joints of the body that normally are not exercised very much in a more active style of asana practice.

Suitable for almost all levels, Yin Yoga is a perfect complement to the dynamic and muscular (yang) styles of yoga that emphasize internal heat, and the lengthening and contracting of our muscles. Yin Yoga generally targets the connective tissues of the hips, pelvis, and lower spine.

Yin Yoga has many amazing benefits but below are some of the key benefits you may begin to feel after a regular yin practice:

-Stillness: calms and balances the mind and body
-Stress and anxiety reduction
-Increased circulation
-Improved flexibility
-Fascial release

WHAT IS YIN YOGA?

Yin Yoga is a style of yoga practice that targets the connective tissues, such as the ligaments, bones, and even the joints of the body that normally are not exercised very much in a more active style of asana practice.

Suitable for almost all levels, Yin Yoga is a perfect complement to the dynamic and muscular (yang) styles of yoga that emphasize internal heat, and the lengthening and contracting of our muscles. Yin Yoga generally targets the connective tissues of the hips, pelvis, and lower spine.

Yin Yoga has many amazing benefits but below are some of the key benefits you may begin to feel after a regular yin practice:

-Stillness: calms and balances the mind and body
-Stress and anxiety reduction
-Increased circulation
-Improved flexibility
-Fascial release

qeyWBFvKQSQ.title: Learn To Headstand & Elbow Stand Easily | Beginner Level To Impressive Yoga Variations
qeyWBFvKQSQ.description:
Anyone can learn how to head stand and elbow stand in a few and easy steps. Through mastering your strength and balance both Sirsasana and Pincha Mayurasana yoga postures can help you take your yoga class to the next level. 

No matter if you are a complete beginner or an advanced yogi this boho beautiful yoga master class is a fun way  to expand your inversions. In this yoga master class we will explore all levels from getting into the most basic version to impressive and challenging variations. 

Inversions, when practiced mindfully, bring so much benefit to the body! Not only do they allow us to explore the body and have some play time with ourselves but they also can relieve anxiety, remove stress and increase focus and self confidence. Inversions stimulate and also cleanse the systems- including increasing the metabolism. So with so much benefit attached to go upside down, adding inversions to our daily yoga practice can be extremely valuable for our health and well being. 

Just be careful. 
DON'T push past your comfort zone.
Listen to your body.
AND make sure to put your weight on your arms NOT your actual head!

OH YEAH... and have FUN!  because head-stands aren't just for the young, they are also for the young at heart!

Fd3Su5lWJsw.title: Full Body Yoga Workout To Feel Alive | 7 Day Challenge For Isolated Times
Fd3Su5lWJsw.description:
This 10 to 15 minute full body yoga workout will tone, strengthen, and stretch your entire body while releasing stress and tension from of your mind at the same time. Its a perfect at home workout for these isolated and uncertain times. 

Click here for all the details & downloadable 7 Day Yoga Workout Calendar/Schedule
 https://bohobeautiful.life/at-home-yoga-workout-schedule/

This at home yoga workout class is the perfect combination of an energizing yoga flow combined with different toning exercises which allow you to not only feel the physical and mental benefits of a home yoga practice but also help you attain those physical goals.

This Boho Beautiful yoga workout practice is what you need to make sure you are including effective and challenging practices on the mat into your daily routine. It is here to remind you to find the time especially in these unsettling moments in our lives and dedicate it to yourself, your wellbeing, and personal growth.

Through the 7 day home yoga workout calendar provided in the link above, your challenge will be to include and complete our new Yoga Workout class but then to also follow it with the second suggested yoga workout practice provided in the calendar to push and challenge the body to the next level. In the time when the COVID-19 pandemic has affected all of our lives and so many of us are staying and working from home, embarking on a weekly challenge like this will not only help you keep your body and mind strong and fluid but it will also help you take your practice to that next level by strengthening the body in so many ways you've never imagined.

So find 30-40 minutes in your day, and virtually escape with us to beautiful beaches and mountains all over the world for your personal yoga workout practice.

Remember, it's always important to pair a healthy diet with your intense work on the mat as diet contributes to 80% of your physical results. So as you embark on this 7 day challenge journey, make sure you are mindful of the fuel that you put into your body.

ENr27Q1hKsw.title: Blissful Yoga Flow For Unsettling Times | Yoga To Find Balance, Strength & Peace At Home
ENr27Q1hKsw.description:
This 15 minute intermediate yoga flow is the perfect and blissful way to find peace at home on your yoga mat, especially during these unsettling times in our world right now. 

With many people in quarantine and feeling the effects of the COVID-19 pandemic affecting their everyday lives, we wanted to provide a yoga class that can help people find balance, peace, and physical and mental strength during such turbulent times. 

This yoga practice will give you the opportunity to release any unwanted energy, stiffness, and tension out of your entire body. This boho beautiful yoga class is great for all levels however intermediate levels will have an easier times in certain pictures. With that said, if you are a beginner feel free to take as many modifications as needed. If you are more advanced, feel free to move and flow through this yoga practice at whatever pace you like. 

This full body yoga class for toning and flexibility is the perfect mixture of standing asanas, movement and posture transitions that will allow you to not only increase your flexibility but also stimulate the metabolism, strengthen your lower body, and allow you to connect deeper with your inner self. This is the perfect practice to welcome the sunset or sunrise which will give you the opportunity to disconnect and reconnect with all that's within. 

Roll out that mat and enjoy! XO

Yoga Instructor: Juliana Spicoluk
Video Creator: Mark Spicoluk

This Boho Beautiful Core Challenge is the day by day guidance that you need to make sure you are including effective and challenging core exercises into your daily workouts in order to achieve your physical fitness goals. 7mi15YbS8wg.title: 25 Min Yin Yoga Class | 7 Day Yin Yoga Exploration Challenge
7mi15YbS8wg.description:
In under 30 minutes a day, take yourself on a beautiful exploration of the style of Yin Yoga and how it can provide your body and mind everything you didn't even know you needed and more. 
Click here to get the FREE 7 Day Yin Yoga Exploration Challenge & Schedule: https://bohobeautiful.life/yin_yoga

Get Our FREE Yoga Handbook eBook: https://bohobeautiful.life/freebooks/

This 30 minute Yin Yoga class for everyone is a perfect way to relax your body and mind and let go of any unwanted tension in your muscles. This easy and gentle yin yoga practice is a beautiful way to deeply stretch your body after a long day, or help let go of any stress and negative energy that may be stored within you. 

This slow and restorative yin yoga practice will not only release physical soreness and stiffness but also welcome any release of emotional and mental stress that you may be holding within the hips and lower body. It's important to surrender to each yin yoga posture and accept any type of emotional release that may come your way. Be patient with your body and let go. 

Remember, breathing is a very important factor in any Yin Yoga class so through out this entire practice make sure you're taking deep breaths in and long slow exhales out. Bring oxygen to your muscles, organs, and mind. Re-energize your nervous system, let go of stress and tension, and become fully present in each moment of each posture as you let go of the past with each exhale you make. 

Roll out that mat and enjoy! XO

What is Yin Yoga?

Yin Yoga is a style of yoga practice that targets the connective tissues, such as the ligaments, bones, and even the joints of the body that normally are not exercised very much in a more active style of asana practice.

Suitable for almost all levels, Yin Yoga is a perfect complement to the dynamic and muscular (yang) styles of yoga that emphasize internal heat, and the lengthening and contracting of our muscles. Yin Yoga generally targets the connective tissues of the hips, pelvis, and lower spine.

Yin Yoga has many amazing benefits but below are some of the key benefits you may begin to feel after a regular yin practice:

-Stillness: calms and balances the mind and body
-Stress and anxiety reduction
-Increased circulation
-Improved flexibility
-Fascial release

uIlgpraQY34.title: Yoga Justice Warriors- Stay Back | The Journey, Ascension, & Division Of Yoga
uIlgpraQY34.description:
Yoga is about union. Not Division. 
My soul honours your soul, in seeing the light and energy within you I recognize that it is also within me, and in this we are the same. We are one.  Namaste

On or off our yoga mats, each and every one of us are on our special personal journey. Yoga can be an incredible tool to further our personal growth.  It in all forms can aid us to find a deeper connection within, no matter what the "method' or 'style' we practice. With the recent popularization of yoga throughout the west and many people including ourselves incorporating it into our own personal livelihood, it triggers a lot of negativity from people who believe it's "their way or the highway". We want to share our opinion on the so called "yoga justice warriors" that feel ok to expel their negativity and division onto others.

xCmQTR8z8j0.title: Wrist Pain During Yoga & Workouts | HOW TO DEAL WITH IT
xCmQTR8z8j0.description:
Wrist pain during yoga and mat based fitness is a common problem. 
We get so many questions asking how to deal with wrist pain, how to cure it, and how to manage it so we created this wrist pain tutorial video for anyone that is looking for an answer. 

Why do my wrists hurt during yoga? How do I strengthen the wrists? What can I do when my wrists become weak and begin to hurt during yoga? How do I hold my planks without wrist pain? 

A lot of the time people experience wrist pain in planks, downward dogs, chaturangas, or just generally when bearing a lot of body weight on their hands. There are ways to cope with this wrist pain by using different wrist strengthening exercises, and wrists stretching movements and postures. 

Try to include these different wrist pain solutions before or after your yoga practice and/or workouts. With time and patience the pain will get less as the body gets stronger. 

We took 10 minutes on set of our new program Boho Beautiful Retreat (http://www.bohobeautiful.life/retreat) and answered some of your questions and concerns about everything to do with wrist pain and how to manage it.

h44voCYC6F4.title: Dreams, Vision Boards, & How To Take Back Control in 2020
h44voCYC6F4.description:
This new year 2020 is a perfect opportunity to set your dreams, visions, and goals back up and in the direction you want. For the last seven years we have been implementing one strategy to take back control of our lives which at the beginning of this wild ride together, seemed so far out of step with what we really wanted from our life. 

But it's not a race. It's clarity. It's creating a map. And every day checking back in on whether or not you are still on course, and then making slight adjustments always. Getting where or what you want out of life, and becoming the person you believe you can be, is a quiet and slow process of many steps. And it is a constant battle with falling down or out of step, understanding it to be a part of the journey, and then recognizing the changes to your behaviour you have to make to get back on track again. Acceptance, forgiveness, perseverance, and most of all: grace. 

That's why every new year we create a vision board.  Also known as a dream board, this single one strategy has allowed us to slowly and methodically design a life and a design for ourselves as people that we are proud to constantly be walking towards. It's not magic. There is no secret. And it takes intense amounts of patience, belief, and determination. 

But most of all after this many years I think the most important idea is that we have found a deep surrender to the process... because the process is the journey... and if you get too comfortable the journey can so easily take control of you, so once in a while you have to spend a little time remembering where it is you want to go, so that you can take back control of it. 

———————————————————————————————————————

yWL8Y49A-iE.description:
This yoga for complete beginners class is perfect for anyone that is new to yoga or needing a very gentle and easy home yoga class at home. This easy gentle Boho Beautiful yoga class is perfect for beginners to release tension out of the upper body, lower body soreness, or to begin to incorporate gentle movement back into your life.

Throughout this gentle yoga practice for all levels, we will breathe, we will disconnect the mind from the daily mental noise and thought patters, giving yourself a moment to be one with yourself. Whether you are a first time yoga practitioner, or someone that is looking for a 15 minute easy yoga practice for stress release, this yoga class will give you that opportunity to take all that you need for your needs. 

Being patient and loving will be the key to this yoga practice today. Surrendering and allowing the postures to take you further into this experience of yoga, self-discovery, and inner peace. 
Remember, breathing is a very important factor in any style of yoga. So bring oxygen to your muscles, organs, and mind. Re-energize your nervous system, let go of stress and tension, and become fully present in each moment of each posture as you let go of the past with each exhale you make. 

#yogaforbeginners  #freeyogavideos #bohobeautifulyoga

Total Body Yoga Flow | Morning Yoga Class: Awaken

This 20 minute yoga class for everyone is the perfect way to awaken the body in the morning or any time of the day when you feel like you need to increase your flow of energy. An online yoga practice that will allow you to strengthen the body and increase flexibility from the comfort of your own home. This yoga vinyasa flow is all about finding the stability and power in your lower body and challenging the core at the same. That’s right this yoga practice for everyone will also work the abs and core of your body through the challenge of balancing and stability yoga asanas and movements. We will flow, we will breathe, increase flexibility, balance, strength, and find that power from within. 

If you are looking to tone and sculpt the body, increase your flexibility, and develop a better balanced practice then this vinyasa yoga flow is for you. 

So grab that mat and enjoy!

IV7rEFOkRkU.title: Yoga For Beginners | Easy 20 Minute Yoga Experience
IV7rEFOkRkU.description:
Yoga For Beginners | Easy 20 Minute Yoga Flow : Boho Beautiful Yoga
This beginner yoga class is for anyone that is looking for a gentle and easy yoga flow. Great for first time yogis as well as everyone looking for a peaceful gentle movement & stretch class that releases the hamstrings, hip flexors, shoulders, and brings peace to the mind. 

Throughout this gentle yoga vinyasa flow we will breathe, we will disconnect the mind from the daily mental noise and thought patters, giving yourself a moment to be one with yourself. Whether you are a first time yoga practitioner, or someone that is looking for a 20 minute deep and gentle stretch, this yoga class will give you that opportunity to take all that you need for your needs. 

Being patient and loving will be the key to this yoga practice today. Surrendering and allowing the postures to take you further into this experience of yoga, self-discovery, and inner peace. 
Remember, breathing is a very important factor in any style of yoga. So bring oxygen to your muscles, organs, and mind. Re-energize your nervous system, let go of stress and tension, and become fully present in each moment of each posture as you let go of the past with each exhale you make.

XzWctoBI-6g.title: Yin Yoga For Upper Body | Release ALL Your Stress In 20 Minutes
XzWctoBI-6g.description:
Yin Yoga For Upper Body | Release All Your Stress In 20 Minutes : Boho Beautiful Yoga
This Yin Yoga class for upper body is going to be fully targeted on releasing tension and stiffness in your neck, shoulders, arms, and upper back. This restorative yoga practice using yin yoga poses to release upper body soreness & stiffness for the physical body, and emotional and mental stress that you may be holding deep within. We will move gently and slowly through each yoga posture and hold selected asanas for two and half minutes to encourage a really deep myofascial release. 

Remember, breathing is a very important factor in any Yin Yoga class so through out this entire practice make sure you're taking deep breaths in and long slow exhales out. Bring oxygen to your muscles, organs, and mind. Re-energize your nervous system, let go of stress and tension, and become fully present in each moment of each posture as you let go of the past with each exhale you make. 

Shot in the beautiful nation of Tibet. 
please check out http://www.freetibet.org

To Get Our Full YIN YOGA Program:
https://bohobeautiful.life/product/essential-yin-yoga-journey/


What is Yin Yoga?

Yin Yoga is a style of yoga practice that targets the connective tissues, such as the ligaments, bones, and even the joints of the body that normally are not exercised very much in a more active style of asana practice.

Suitable for almost all levels, Yin Yoga is a perfect complement to the dynamic and muscular (yang) styles of yoga that emphasize internal heat, and the lengthening and contracting of our muscles. Yin Yoga generally targets the connective tissues of the hips, pelvis, and lower spine.

Yin Yoga has many amazing benefits but below are some of the key benefits you may begin to feel after a regular yin practice:

-Stillness: calms and balances the mind and body
-Stress and anxiety reduction
-Increased circulation
-Improved flexibility
-Fascial release

Enjoy and let go of all that no longer serves you,

Juliana & Mark 
#BohoBeautiful #YogaForStiffness #YinYoga

cN8p_wzblzA.title: Best Yoga For You | A Wonderful Yoga Class In Magical Tibet
cN8p_wzblzA.description:
Best Yoga For You | Boho Beautiful Yoga 
This 15 minute yoga class is best explained simply as a wonderful yoga class for you. It's a perfect for morning stimulation or evening wind down, and it is a great stretch for sore muscles.  Not too easy and not too hard, this peaceful and grounded yogic journey is a great class for almost anyone of any level and stage in their yoga journey that is looking to release general stress, tension, and anxiety out of their physical body as well as their mental state of being. This yoga class is for everyone and anyone that is looking to unwind after a stressful day or needs a way to find grounding and centering before they start their day. So this is a great morning and evening gentle yoga practice that will leave you feeling open, flexible, and more relaxed. 

While remaining with your conscious breath & awareness through each movement, this yoga class will have you moving through different hip, hamstrings, and glute postures to increase flexibility and release tension within. 

Remember to be patient with your body and never force any posture. This yoga class is intended to make you feel great and relaxed by the end. Do your best and never force anything. Simply surrender to the idea that you are exactly where you are supposed to be, and that with time, patience, dedication, and hard work your body will naturally respond and increase in flexibility, strength, and fluidity.

So roll out that mat and have fun. 

Namaste xx

Juliana

FQxNE5GWZ3o.title: Beginner Yoga For Hips & Hamstrings | Best Relief For Stiff & Sore Muscles
FQxNE5GWZ3o.description:
This 15 minute Boho Beautiful beginner yoga class is going to be all about releasing tension and stiffness out of your hips. Through gentle movement, this yoga practice for beginners and all levels will focus on increasing flexibility in your hamstrings, stretching different areas of your glute muscles, and opening the hips. The postures will go deep and we will be stimulating a lot of physical and emotional release of energy of your body so remember to always be gentle and patient with yourself. Always remember to breathe and stay with your breath. As we go deeper into hip opening yoga asanas, your breath is going to allow you to stay present and release deeper and deeper with time. 

Remember to always listen to your body. If you develop any sharp or shooting pain, take a pause and reset yourself. Never force any postures, but rather simply allow yourself to surrender once you get into a pose. Coming into a meditative state of mind as you hold and let go. 

So get ready to stretch, release, and dive deeper into your hips and hamstrings. 

Namaste xx

Juliana 

Location: Mardi Himal Trek, Nepal

6BQH1-tG61A.title: Wake Up Yoga For All | Yoga For Harmony, Strength & Inner Power
6BQH1-tG61A.description:
This 20 minute yoga class for strength and inner power is an incredible way to energize your body, wake up your mind, and increase your flexibility. It is a perfect yoga class for mornings, but also this yoga flow is wonderful for inner alignment, an energy refresh, or to recharge and lift yourself at any point.  

While remaining with your conscious breath & awareness through each movement, this yoga class will have you moving through different planks, chaturangas, warrior asanas, and overall body movement. This yoga flow for strength and energy will allow you to build incredible strength in your lower body and shoulders. As you flow through each movement, remember to stay connected to your breath. Anytime the yoga poses become challenging, taking that extra breath of oxygen to re-generate your cells, and muscular stamina will be crucial. 
Remember to be patient with your body and never force any posture. This yoga class is geared for more intermediate level yogis so if you are new to yoga, take as many modifications as you need. Do your best and never force anything. Simply surrender to the idea that you are exactly where you are supposed to be, and that with time, patience, dedication, and hard work your body will naturally respond and increase in flexibility, strength, stamina, and endurance. 

So roll out that mat. Work hard and have fun. 

Namaste xx

Yoga Instructor: Juliana Spicoluk
Video Creator: Mark Spicoluk

Location: Mardi Himal Trek, Nepal 
#Yoga #BohoBeautiful #MorningYoga #YogaToToneTheBody

IFSp2-CmQvk.title: Ashtanga Inspired Yoga | Morning Flow With Intermediate Binds
IFSp2-CmQvk.description:
This 20 minute Ashtanga inspired intermediate yoga class will start your day perfectly and challenge your practice to help advance to a new level.

While remaining with your conscious breath & awareness through each movement, this morning yoga class will start out with an Ashtanga Surya Namaskar B sun salutation to get the body moving. Then the practice will move through many variations of yogic squats, forward folds, inversions, and more to stimulate and wake-up your body. This intermediate yoga flow will involve many binds to boost your digestive system, increase your metabolism, and get you ready to start your day. 

Remember to be patient with your body and never force any posture. This is an intermediate yoga class that is for anyone that wants to advance their yoga asanas and challenge their body in a different way. Remember to use your Ujayi breathing to keep the mind and body steady and focused. Releasing all the toxins and negativity with each breath. 

Namaste xx

Juliana

pThXSdN-kaA.title: When We Stopped Everything To Live With Monks ♥ Boho Diary | Kopan Monastery
pThXSdN-kaA.description:
We found a beautiful way to spend less travelling and acquire more. Not more in experience, but more in depth. Nepal backpack travel offers so many unique ways to experience the incredible culture, mountains, trekking, and the overall Nepalese way of life. So we decided to start our backpacking Asia trip by bringing our lives to a screeching halt and committing 10 days to a Tibetan Buddhist Monastery. Our lives sometimes seem out of control. All about our devices, all about our channel, all about focussing away from ourselves and too much towards things that have unconsciously sucked us in... so every now and then we have to do something to stop and find the reset button. To breathe and to look inside again, and see what is left to be discovered. And there is always so much. 

So there we were. At Kopan Monastery living, eating, and meditatiting with all the other students, and  hundreds of Tibetan monks while taking a Discovering Buddhism Course. What a wild, deep, and meaningful experience. 

At times it was tough... structured religion and dogmatic plausible contractictions.  And at other times it was perspective altering and incredibly valuable to our own spirituality. Just like anything in life, we took what we needed from this wonderful experience of monk life. We discovered the fundamentals of Tibetan Buddhism that placed a lot of life into a beautiful perspective. We cried, we laughed, we were challenged, and we overcame it everything that was brought forward to learn a little bit more of what our Boho Beautiful life is all about.

_B1_3CS9pj4.title: SOCIETY SUCKS SOULS | We Made An Escape Plan & Walked Away 🏔 Boho Diary Nepal
_B1_3CS9pj4.description:
It's been just over 3 years since we started this channel on a hell bent mission to change our life. We were definitely unhappy and felt the direction of the path that we were headed on wasn't what our souls were asking for. We knew there was more to life than Toronto. More to things than the ego driven rat race we had found ourselves participating in. So we designed, alchemised, and began our escape. 

This journey has been a roller-coaster of extremes. But so far it has been more fulfilling, exciting, & beautiful a ride than we ever believed we could ask for. 

As we hiked the incredible mountain of Mardi Himal in Nepal, our minds began to go back in time and reflect on this journey that we've set upon. 

Thank you to our friends at Rugged Trails Nepal for the wonderful trip and guidance!
Check Them Out If You Are Looking For A Personalized Hiking Trip in Nepal!!
https://www.ruggedtrailsnepal.com 

May this travel blog/boho diary of our difficult Mardi Himal trek inspire anyone out there that is itching to find a way any situation that doesn't fill them up. Our society at times can feel like a cage, prisoning us in a cycle of debt, bills, mortgage payments, and the constant fear that we don't have enough. Just know there is always a way out, and if there's this burn in your heart and you feel like your soul is being killed by the constant pressures of our western world then take moment and realize that anything is possible and that you too can figure out a way to pack up and leave. 
We meet people all the time that quit their corporate jobs and move to an island or a smaller town with a slower pace of life. They start a small business, an ice cream shop, they make jewelry and sell it on etsy, they run airbnb's or life coaching online business, etc..etc.

Times are not what they used to be 20 years ago, the boom of the internet has opened the door for so many self made entrepreneurs to be born. So if there's an itch in your heart and a whisper in your soul. Don't drown out the noise, but instead listen closely as it will guide you how to break free and find all that it longs for. 

Love & Light,

Juliana and Mark

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

By donating any amount that you can to Kate and Doug's Organization, it will ensure that they have the funds needed to continue taking care of the sick, abandoned, and mistreated animals on the streets of Nepal.

Our love and hearts go out to all the people in Nepal and the people around the world fighting the good fight for all the sentient and helpless human and non-human creatures of this Earth. Thank you for standing up for what’s right, for not walking away and leaving someone else to deal with the problem, and for opening your heart to those that need us most. May we all live our lives with more love and compassion.

FlmtfcPmHFg.description:
My soul is not contained within the limits of my body, my body is contained within the limitlessness of my soul. -Jim Carrey

This idea has been on my mind for a while now. How our appearance, the way we look, the way we dress, the job we hold, all of these and more create this identity that we tend to become attached to. An attachment that later on begins to bring anxiety and stress into our life as we begin to witness this body of ours change. And that's the thing, change....the undeniable truth that each and everyone one of us will encounter. The more we realize that we are not these bodies, that we are not these avatars that we create, but that we are so much greater than our surface. We are energy that was energy before we came into this life and consciousness, and we are the energy that will remain after our eventual end. Once we truly accept that, maybe we can realize that life is just play and that this beautiful existence is simply just one incredible dance and experience in itself.

W5rMIoqCZug.description:
This 20 minute yoga flow class for beginners and advanced students is the perfect combination of movement, stillness, and breath. Focusing on the Earth Element of Air, this vinyasa based yoga class for all levels will allow you to truly connect with that inner universal life force, your prana. As we move through the gentle flow and standing yoga asanas I want you to constantly focus on deepening your inhalation and exhalation. Allowing your mind the opportunity to find the present moment through your practice. 

The element of air is all about movement, creativity, and that deeper realization that we are all a part of something greater than us. So as you slowly move and relax into this yoga practice for stress release, allow yourself to connect deeper with all that is within you. Be patient, take very yoga pose modification that you may need, breathe, and let go. This yoga is to help you let go of anything that may no longer serve you, whether that is anxiety, stress, negativity, or overall tension. So let all that energy go with each breath and enjoy. xo

d7cX_NRCHvY.description:
This 20 minute Yoga Vinyasa Flow class is perfect to get your body moving and flowing. An easy vinyasa fluid flow that will target your balance, strength, and coordination. With the focus on the Earth element of water, this all levels online yoga class will allow you to truly work on connecting your breath to each and every move. Using the pranayama practice of Ujayi breath, as you move through this practice I want you to focus on finding that present moment by mimicking the sound of the ocean with each exhalation. With this exhalation letting go of all that no longer serves you, letting go of that negative energy and welcome beautiful and radiant positive energy every time you take that breath in. 

Focus, let go, and enjoy the flow. 

Love & Light...
Juliana & Mark**

fAAD8gCgxSk.description:
Do You Want To Apply To Be Part Of The Boho Beautiful Team? 
Click the link and see if you're what were looking for:
https://bohobeautiful.life/jobposting 

Click The Link Below For Our New Program: https://bohobeautiful.life/transform/ 

Its been a wild year for us and as we began to experience a familiar situation used across the Youtube Platform these days..."Creator Burn Out". Youtubers seem to burning out like crazy these days- Youtube burn out has been creeping into our lives now too, so we decided to make some big changes. 

So as we welcome this incredible milestone into our journey,  it's important to always be self aware of how the demands of anything you do in life play on your mental and physical well being. By all means there's no day that goes by that we're not extremely grateful for all that has been brought to us through the Boho Beautiful community but we're also now starting to take some time to make space, recharge the batteries, re-evaluate our priorities so that we can welcome more and exciting projects into our life.

eiQjt0WSVHk.title: Back Pain & Sciatica Relief ♥ Your Daily Yoga Miracle Therapy
eiQjt0WSVHk.description:
New Full Length Fitness Program: https://bohobeautiful.life/transform/

This 30 minute gentle yoga class is designed specifically for anyone suffering from back pain, sciatica pain, or lower body soreness. With a gentle increase of movement, yoga postures, therapeutic strength exercises we will be gently stimulating the back  muscles, stretching the glutes and hamstrings and giving our body an opportunity to move with care. This yoga class for back pain is also great for anyone suffering from bulging disks or disk herniation.  
Its very important that you listen to your body and if your body responds well to these types of exercises include them into your life everyday. The glutei stretches are great for loosing up the muscles in case your nerve is pinched in that area. The back exercises which include in gentle extensions are great for anyone suffering from disk herniation or bulging disks. Try to do these everyday to strengthen the muscles around the spine, however avoid rounding out the spine and perhaps even skip the child pose if you do suffer from disk injuries.With daily commitment, with time you will begin to feel an improvement in your back and nerve pain.

During this yoga class for all levels, you will allow your mind and body to connect deeper inward, letting go of any worries or stressful thoughts and truly giving your mind and body the gift of mindful movement, stillness, and healing.  Enjoy and breathe. 

Love & Light...
Juliana & Mark**

https://lumeriamaui.com

i2qG4weEbLo.title: Yoga To Advance Your Practice ♥ Beautiful Ashtanga Inspired Flow
i2qG4weEbLo.description:
New Full Length Fitness Program-  https://bohobeautiful.life/transform 

This advanced yoga class is here to allow you to take your personal yoga practice to the next level. An ashtanga fusion yoga class will heat up your body through a sequence of sun salutations and then allow your body to go deeper into different yoga postures which will show you the option between intermediate and advanced level of asanas. While challenging the body to push its physical limitation, this online yoga class will also allow your mind to focus and be still as you concentrate on the present moment and your breath as you flow through this class.

Remember to be patient with yourself. This advanced yoga class can be hard in many moments, so please listen to your body and only push yourself to a limit that you are comfortable with. If you incorporate this yoga workout practice and its postures into your daily practice, we promise that you will begin to see incredible changes in your strength and stamina of the body. 

Get ready to challenge yourself, breathe, and stretch! XO

Juliana and Mark*

4IeS84sb3ZQ.title: Yin Yoga For Flexibility ♥ A Sore Hip & Hamstring Love Song
4IeS84sb3ZQ.description:
To Get The Full Yin Yoga Program:
https://bohobeautiful.life/product/essential-yin-yoga-journey/ 

This 20 minute Yin Yoga class is the perfect way to release tension and stress out of your hips as well as increase flexibility in your hamstrings and inner thighs. This slow and restorative yin yoga practice will not only release physical soreness and stiffness but also welcome any release of emotional and mental stress that you may be holding within the hip area of your body. It's important to surrender to each yin yoga posture and accept any type of emotional release that may come your way. Be patient with your body and let go. 

Remember, breathing is a very important factor in any Yin Yoga class so through out this entire practice make sure you're taking deep breaths in and long slow exhales out. Bring oxygen to your muscles, organs, and mind. Re-energize your nervous system, let go of stress and tension, and become fully present in each moment of each posture as you let go of the past with each exhale you make. 


What is Yin Yoga?

Yin Yoga is a style of yoga practice that targets the connective tissues, such as the ligaments, bones, and even the joints of the body that normally are not exercised very much in a more active style of asana practice.

Suitable for almost all levels, Yin Yoga is a perfect complement to the dynamic and muscular (yang) styles of yoga that emphasize internal heat, and the lengthening and contracting of our muscles. Yin Yoga generally targets the connective tissues of the hips, pelvis, and lower spine.

Yin Yoga has many amazing benefits but below are some of the key benefits you may begin to feel after a regular yin practice:

-Stillness: calms and balances the mind and body
-Stress and anxiety reduction
-Increased circulation
-Improved flexibility
-Fascial release

Enjoy and let go of all that no longer serves you,

Juliana & Mark 
#BohoBeautiful #Yoga #YinYoga

iUxr6KpdggA.description:
We got tattoos together. In Ubud Indonesia last summer. And all that we are completely sure of is that the stars aligned and then we followed our hearts. 

Learn More About Yayasan Widya Guna Learning Centre & sponsor a child today! http://www.yayasanwidyaguna.org/welcome.html 

Big thank you to Concious Arts Tattoo Shop and Agus for your energy and incredible work! 
https://www.consciousartstattoos.com 
https://www.instagram.com/tattoos_by_agus

We travelled to Ubud, Bali to work with the best tattoo artist we found online which could create beautiful spiritual imagery with vegan tattoo ink on our bodies. Getting a tattoo is a decision you make that will last a lifetime, so we really had to tune in deeper to find the right person, the right tattoo shop with the right energy to, and of course artwork that spoke to our souls. We believe Conscious Arts Tattoo Shop in Ubud Bali and Agus was the winning combination for us. Agus' dot and mandala work and the ethics of the Balinese Tattoo Shop. Tattoo art is a way to confirm our beliefs, convictions, and emotion through ink to ourselves in the future, and when we met Agus and saw what he could do we knew it was a perfect fit. That he was capable of helping create the perfect reminder for ourselves. Tatoo art to remind us to never look back and to continue to fight for progress in ourselves and the world around us every single day.

New Full Length Fitness Program-  https://bohobeautiful.life/transform 

This 10 minute cardio workout class is an amazing and effective way to boost your metabolism, stimulate fat loss, and tone every muscle in your body in a very short amount of time. Weather you are short on time and need something fast and effective, or you are ready to take on a challenge and include this workout into your daily fitness schedule for the next 7 days.  After completing 1-2 rounds of this fat burning HIIT cardio class, your body will be in its ultimate “fat burning zone”, which means as you begin to work through the other toning and sculpting classes you will be burning that unwanted fat and building lean and healthy muscles in an accelerated rate.

When completed as part of the 7 Day Cardio Challenge, the results that you will see and feel will be unbelievable! But remember, you are exactly where you need to be in your own personal fitness journey, so cater this challenge to your own body and strength. If you need to pause the video mid way to take a break, do so. If you need to do only the 1 round through for the whole week, do that as well. No matter what modifications you take, as long as you get through it at your own level, consider that a successful challenge! As you succeed through each day, you will begin to notice that the class gets easier which in truth isn’t the case…it is only YOU who is getting stronger. So if you’re ready to boost your metabolism, burn fat, and get yourself feeling amazing get on that mat and press play!

This 20 minute Astanga inspired Yoga Workout Practice is perfect for anyone that is looking to strengthen the body and build their stamina and cardio. Using the Ashtanga primary series Surya Namaskar B sun salutations to warm up the body and different strengthening yoga asanas this yoga workout class will help increase your metabolism, stimulate fat loss, and release any tension and stiffness out of your entire body. 

Remember to be patient with yourself. Astanga can be hard on your practice at times, so please listen to your body and only push yourself to a limit that you are comfortable with. If you incorporate this yoga workout practice and its postures into your daily practice, we promise that you will begin to see incredible changes in your strength and stamina of the body. 

Get ready to tone, breathe, and stretch! XO

Juliana and Mark

lTcQSKVTyqA.title: The 1100 Dogs of Territorio De Zaguates ♥ Everyone Needs Healing- Land Of Strays
lTcQSKVTyqA.description:
Please Join Us To Help Territorio De Zaguates Dog Sanctuary!!
CLICK HERE TO DONATE: https://www.gofundme.com/bohostrays/

TO SHIP GOODS TO TERRITORIO DE ZAGUATES: 
Please make sure you label all parcels as a GIFT VALUED UNDER $500. Otherwise there will be extra taxes added that the sanctuary is unable to pay to receive your gifts. 

Shipping Label: 
Territorio de Zaguates (Land Of The Strays)
PO Box: 782-1260
Plaza Colonial, Escazu
Costa Rica

Territorio de Zaguates aka Land Of The Strays is a place like non-other.  378 acres of mountainous fields where 1000's of stray, injured, and abused dogs have come over the last 12 years to learn be dogs again. The ultimate goal here is to find homes for them all, but the beauty of Land Of The Strays is that if they don't find a family it's the perfect place for them to all live their rest of days together in freedom and happiness. 

All the dogs that have come to this beautiful sanctuary have experienced some kind of human inflicted suffering and abandonment, but here they are given a second chance. The cruelty that is done to so many of these innocent beings is unthinkable yet the compassion that Lya and her team give to these dogs everyday finds a way to heal them. With Territorio De Zaguates' numbers now rising to over 1100 free roaming dogs, the costs are rising too and Land Of The Strays needs our help. 

It costs approximately $36 dollars/month to take care of 1 dog . They always rely on financial assistance and donations for all food, staff, and veterinary expenses but at the moment they're also in desperate need of help to cover the following expenses:

Completion of more enclosures and roofing.
A morgue.
Extensive Drainage and runoff modifications.
Elevate the entire extension of the eating troughs.
Build a properly equipped "clinic" area where the doctor can operate.
A shed only for cleaning materials.
A shed only for medicine.
Tags for all dogs.

ALSO- Aside from all of this, they are unfortunately in the need of equipping the entire living area of the dogs as well as the entrance to the farm with cameras and movement sensor lamps because they have recently been getting many trespassers who try to poison their dogs at night! This is requiring them to extend the original electrical layout to far regions of the area in order to secure their land from intruders, which represents a HUGE expense. 

So we ask that you open your heart to whatever you can. Nothing is too little for them and every little bit helps.  
Even just a few dollars doesn't make a difference to our individual day to day lives but to these dogs and to Lya it means the world. 

We ask that you stand with us and help Territorio de Zaguates thrive and continue to save the lives of the all the innocent pups that they are fighting to rescue every day. 

Lets support good people doing good things. 
You and I may not be able to change the entire world but together we can change the entire world of each of these dogs that is currently fighting for his/her life. 

Thank you for standing with us. Thank you for standing up for these dogs. 

And thank you for your love and support! 

Website: https://www.territoriodezaguates.com/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/territoriodezaguates/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/territorio_de_zaguates/
Youtube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCvHc3BIZdnloZ9gVDv7fX2g

Check Out Our Friends Who Helped Us Make this Beautiful Video Libby & Marcel:
Youtube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCAot4d6MBEKKnPaMeGM289w
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/libbyandmarcel/

localized.title: The 1100 Dogs of Territorio De Zaguates ♥ Everyone Needs Healing- Land Of Strays
localized.description:
Please Join Us To Help Territorio De Zaguates Dog Sanctuary!!
CLICK HERE TO DONATE: https://www.gofundme.com/bohostrays/

TO SHIP GOODS TO TERRITORIO DE ZAGUATES: 
Please make sure you label all parcels as a GIFT VALUED UNDER $500. Otherwise there will be extra taxes added that the sanctuary is unable to pay to receive your gifts. 

Shipping Label: 
Territorio de Zaguates (Land Of The Strays)
PO Box: 782-1260
Plaza Colonial, Escazu
Costa Rica

Territorio de Zaguates aka Land Of The Strays is a place like non-other.  378 acres of mountainous fields where 1000's of stray, injured, and abused dogs have come over the last 12 years to learn be dogs again. The ultimate goal here is to find homes for them all, but the beauty of Land Of The Strays is that if they don't find a family it's the perfect place for them to all live their rest of days together in freedom and happiness. 

All the dogs that have come to this beautiful sanctuary have experienced some kind of human inflicted suffering and abandonment, but here they are given a second chance. The cruelty that is done to so many of these innocent beings is unthinkable yet the compassion that Lya and her team give to these dogs everyday finds a way to heal them. With Territorio De Zaguates' numbers now rising to over 1100 free roaming dogs, the costs are rising too and Land Of The Strays needs our help. 

It costs approximately $36 dollars/month to take care of 1 dog . They always rely on financial assistance and donations for all food, staff, and veterinary expenses but at the moment they're also in desperate need of help to cover the following expenses:

Completion of more enclosures and roofing.
A morgue.
Extensive Drainage and runoff modifications.
Elevate the entire extension of the eating troughs.
Build a properly equipped "clinic" area where the doctor can operate.
A shed only for cleaning materials.
A shed only for medicine.
Tags for all dogs.

ALSO- Aside from all of this, they are unfortunately in the need of equipping the entire living area of the dogs as well as the entrance to the farm with cameras and movement sensor lamps because they have recently been getting many trespassers who try to poison their dogs at night! This is requiring them to extend the original electrical layout to far regions of the area in order to secure their land from intruders, which represents a HUGE expense. 

So we ask that you open your heart to whatever you can. Nothing is too little for them and every little bit helps.  
Even just a few dollars doesn't make a difference to our individual day to day lives but to these dogs and to Lya it means the world. 

We ask that you stand with us and help Territorio de Zaguates thrive and continue to save the lives of the all the innocent pups that they are fighting to rescue every day. 

Lets support good people doing good things. 
You and I may not be able to change the entire world but together we can change the entire world of each of these dogs that is currently fighting for his/her life. 

Thank you for standing with us. Thank you for standing up for these dogs. 

And thank you for your love and support!

0JJ1NrwwUvU.title: The Commercialism Plague, We Just Can't  Handle It Anymore ♥ Boho Diary | Peru
0JJ1NrwwUvU.description:
http://www.bohobeautiful.life

Travelling through the magical cities and villages of Peru's Sacred Valley was incredible. It was such an eye opening experience to be immersed in the Peruvian Inca culture, to meet so many wonderful local people, and to hear their stories of how they truly feel about this commercial boom that has been steadily transforming their world. The exploitation of their sacred plant medicine which is now offered on almost every corner, Starbucks taking out the local coffee shops, McDonalds providing jobs but at the same time destroying other local restaurants, and so many foreign companies creeping their way in to siphon so many dollars away. All of this to serve the massive amount of growing travellers descending upon their sacred spaces.  

So what's the best way to travel in Peru? Or anywhere for that matter? How do you experience the Sacred Valley but at the same time not support the elimination of their culture by the commercialistic ways of the Western world? Should we all just stay at home? Is it better to leave it all be and read about our wonderful world only in Nat Geo? Is there a solution? 

We believe there is. And not just abroad, but in our own communities too. Shop local wherever you go, support community businesses, contribute to the culture that you are surrounding yourself with. Vote with your dollars to keep them in the pockets of those who need it most. And realize that the world has so much to offer with its deep diversity and endless cultural beauty that taking a chance on something new is far more rewarding than the safe familiar road. Its up to all of us. What we value, we can keep alive. 

Lek & Save Elephant Foundation:
http://www.saveelephant.org

Happy Cow App & Website!
http://www.happycow.com

Fabrizio's Amazing Adventure:
http://www.luvburger.com

The magic rock garden and waterfall were in Mandor, a beautiful botanical garden and nature reserve that you can add to your bucket list when visiting Machu Picchu. To learn more about this beautiful haven please visit: http://www.jardinesdemandor.com

W51hHB1eynk.title: AMAZON Rainforest Eco-Bootcamp ♥ A Day In The Life
W51hHB1eynk.description:
Welcome to the Amazon Rainforest of Peru. Surrounded by amazonian jungle, tucked away on the Amazon River, we filmed this Day In The Life video at the Otorongo Eco-Lodge - whose mission statement is "Promoting the sustainable development of the environment in the Peruvian Amazon since 2016."  Eco-tourism adventure at its finest. 
During this day in our life consisted of amazon jungle rainforest hiking, a fruit tour, swimming in the amazon river next to the pink and grey amazon river dolphins, a night river terror expedition in which we got both stuck and seemingly lost, sunrise amazon bird watching, searchign for tarantulas and poison frogs, and so much more. 

This sustainable eco lodge allowed us not only live in a sustainable and environmentally friendly way but also experience the Amazon in its raw and pure form. We also got to shoot a couple yoga videos too. 

Come along with us and see what a day in the life in the Amazon basin looks like!

localized.title: AMAZON Rainforest Eco-Bootcamp ♥ A Day In The Life
localized.description:
Welcome to the Amazon Rainforest of Peru. Surrounded by amazonian jungle, tucked away on the Amazon River, we filmed this Day In The Life video at the Otorongo Eco-Lodge - whose mission statement is "Promoting the sustainable development of the environment in the Peruvian Amazon since 2016."  Eco-tourism adventure at its finest. 
During this day in our life consisted of amazon jungle rainforest hiking, a fruit tour, swimming in the amazon river next to the pink and grey amazon river dolphins, a night river terror expedition in which we got both stuck and seemingly lost, sunrise amazon bird watching, searchign for tarantulas and poison frogs, and so much more. 

This sustainable eco lodge allowed us not only live in a sustainable and environmentally friendly way but also experience the Amazon in its raw and pure form. We also got to shoot a couple yoga videos too. 

Come along with us and see what a day in the life in the Amazon basin looks like!

#BohoBeautiful #DayInTheLife #Amazon

DYQHo7OboEM.title: Yin Yoga For Flexibility ♥ Tight Hips & Hamstrings | Sacred Valley
DYQHo7OboEM.description:
To Get The Full Program:
http://www.bohobeautiful.life/complete/ 

This Yin Yoga class is going to give you that relaxing deep stretch your body has been craving for. Focusing on deep hip opening yoga postures this class will allow you to release tension and stress that you've been holding within that area of your body as well as help you gain more flexibility in your hips and hamstrings. The perfect yoga class to paid with any of our Pilates workouts or your own personal workout programs. 


Remember, breathing is a very important factor in any Yin Yoga class so through out this entire practice make sure you're taking deep breaths in and long slow exhales out. Bring oxygen to your muscles, organs, and mind. Re-energize your nervous system, let go of stress and tension, and become fully present in each moment of each posture as you let go of the past with each exhale you make. 


What is Yin Yoga?

Yin Yoga is a style of yoga practice that targets the connective tissues, such as the ligaments, bones, and even the joints of the body that normally are not exercised very much in a more active style of asana practice.

Suitable for almost all levels, Yin Yoga is a perfect complement to the dynamic and muscular (yang) styles of yoga that emphasize internal heat, and the lengthening and contracting of our muscles. Yin Yoga generally targets the connective tissues of the hips, pelvis, and lower spine.

Each posture in Yin Yoga is usually held up to 5 min or so. However, if you're very new to this I recommend you start with the 1-2 min holds until you feel more confident in your posture. If you're more of an advanced yogi then feel free to pause the video and hold each pose longer. 

Yin Yoga has many amazing benefits but below are some of the key benefits you may begin to feel after a regular yin practice:

-Stillness: calms and balances the mind and body
-Stress and anxiety reduction
-Increased circulation
-Improved flexibility
-Fascial release

Enjoy and let go of all that no longer serves you,

Juliana & Mark 
#BohoBeautiful #Yoga #YinYoga

DWdA-WkNmEM.title: Party In The Jungle ♥ Envision Festival 2018 | The Shift
DWdA-WkNmEM.description:
We are really happy to have been able to go to Envision Festival 2018 an annual festival put on in Uvita, right here in Costa Rica! We came into it with no idea of what to expect and were surprisingly blown away but the amazing energy that filled this entire festival. 

From the Envision Fest yoga classes, to the inspiring talks and speeches, amazing vegan food, their garbage program that leaves no waste behind after the festival is done, and of course our favourite Xavier Rudd. We hope that there will continue to be more festivals like this that raise the conciseness of the people, that provide gatherings for like minded people, and that honour the guiding divine light that leads us along our paths. Thank you for this unforgettable time Envision Festival, we will be back!

FvaPi2JjnFI.title: THIS Juice Cleanse ♥ My Story, Weight Loss, & New Me
FvaPi2JjnFI.description:
It’s very important that throughout our life we always find a way to challenge ourselves. Whether that is our body, our mind or both. Starting a juice cleanse was my first challenge of this year and wow was it an intense journey. It first started as a 3 Day Juice Cleanse and then as day 3 arrived I really felt amazing results, so I kept going and made my 3 day Cleanse to a 7 day Raw Juice Cleanse.


JUICE RECIPES

THE GREEN SUNRISE 
This juice is a great way to start your morning off. It's a heavy vegetable juice with a ton of dense nutrients and a great flavour to help push your body to realize that even with out solid food it can still get all that it needs.

Broccoli- 1/2 a stock of broccoli (stem and all)
Spinach- 1/2 a bunch of spinach
Passion Fruit- Entire fruit (no skin!)
Lemon- 1/2 lemon (rinds and seeds)
Cuccumber- 1/2 to 3/4 cucumber
Add ice to make it come alive. 

THE GREEN BULLET
This juice was awesome. I had it everyday at 11am as a natural sugar life (the pinnacle) and internal reboot (the cayenne). 

Kale - 1/2 a bunch
Ginger- a little chunk
Lemon - 1/2 lemon including seeds and rind
Pineapple - 1/4 to 1/2 a pineapple 
Cucumber- 1/2 to 3/4 of cucumber
Top and stir in 1 table spoon of Cayenne Pepper 
Add ice to really make it refresh.

TUMMERIC FOR DAYS
The main purpose of this juice is the turmeric. Its great for so many reasons (google it!) but I love it for my back as an anti inflammatory. This juice was nice in the afternoon and always seemed to hit the spot. 

Orange- 1 oranges
Lemon- 1/2 lemon
Spinach- 1/4 bunch
Carrot- 2 decent sized carrots
Watermelon- 3 big slices
Turmeric-  As much as I could put in without killing the flavour completely
Fresh Black Pepper- Top the finished juice with a half table spoon of black pepper to supercharge and activate the turmeric. 
Finish with ice cubes to cool it down and make it really enjoyable. 


LIQUID V8 
This was one of the staple dinner juices I worked at getting better and better. The key was experimenting to flavours I would like and trying different combinations of nutrient heavy vegetables. It would usually be the last juice of the day and let my body know once again that it can feel full, nourished, and receive more than it needs in liquid form. 

Tomato- 1 full tomato
Broccoli- 1/2 a stock of broccoli (stock included)
Sweet Pepper- Entire pepper (green, red, or yellow)
Spinach - 1/2 a bunch 
Celery- 2 stalks of celery
Carrot- 2 decent size carrots
Beet- 3/4 beet

jaYqvFHmSZo.title: My Raw Vegan Diet ♥  What I Ate & Why It's Not For Me
jaYqvFHmSZo.description:
The Boho Beautiful Vegan Food and Diet approach. Our experience with being Raw Vegan in Costa Rica.

This was my journey on trying to live Raw Vegan for 7 days. It's important to challenge your body from time to time to truly allow yourself to understand what your body needs to thrive at its best. It's hard to say that one type of eating habit will work for everyone as all of our bodies work in different ways. As long as our choices do not harm our planet and/or take away freedom and peace from sentient beings, I believe it's important to try and experiment with different ways of nourishing ourselves to understand the best way we individually can thrive. 

Yoga & Spiritual Music Mixes By DJ Hawk:
https://m.mixcloud.com/chris-hawk/

Frozen Bananas

1tsp Coconut Oil

Mangos
Passion fruits

DkKGTgYt5Dk.title: Guided Meditation For Strength & Grounding ♥ 15 Minutes
DkKGTgYt5Dk.description:
This guided meditation is perfect for any moments when you feel under stress, pressure, or overwhelmed. Taking 15 minutes out of your day to just breathe, be still, and simply be. Shot next to a beautiful La Fortuna waterfall in Costa Rica, this meditation will allow you to to truly look deeper within and let go of any energy that doesn't serve you. A meditation for beginners and all levels and spiritual paths that will help you not only release tension and stress but it will also allow you to begin to deepen your practice in mindfulness and to train your mind for calm detachment from any unwanted patterns of over-thinking.  


By practicing these mindful techniques of conscious observation and self acceptance, you will find you are more able to quiet the mind and truly give yourself permission to dedicate time in your day for your mind and soul. 

Put on some headphones, close your eyes, and enjoy this 15 minute guided meditation.  

love & light,

Juliana and Mark

iWjRCMB_mzY.title: Pilates Intense Mat Workout ♥ Tools For A New You | BELIEF
iWjRCMB_mzY.description:
This class is one of the most effective pilates workout videos we have created for both beginners and advanced. A floor Pilates workout that targets and fine tones different areas of your body which includes your core, obliques, glutes, and hamstrings. Pilates is an incredible way to accomplish real results, weather it's pilates for weight loss, pilates for core strength, or pilates for toning, you can accomplish so much for your body through this circuit of incredibly effective pilates exercises. 

This week the idea we are focussing on in Tools For A New You is ‘belief’. What you think about is what you become. Our minds are so powerful, and one of the key ideas that we must always keep within ourselves especially when we embark on any transformational journey is truly believing in ourselves and our strength. In life we will be met with resistance in many shapes and sizes. Weather that is our body’s limitations, the people around us, or your own ego telling you that achieving your goal is not possible for someone like “you”. Take a deep breath, and allow those thoughts or people around you to fade away as background noise. Find the strength within yourself and believe that no matter how hard it gets, you are strong enough and capable of achieving anything you put your mind into. Always reminding yourself that as long as you believe in it, as long as you are putting all the hard work and energy into your goals and dreams nothing can stop you from achieving that which you deserve, not even your mind. So brush off the negative self talk, pick yourself up if you fall down, and never stop believing in the idea that you deserve to live a happy, healthy, and prosperous existence.

SoymL3XAHWk.title: Gentle Yin Yoga ♥ Tools For A New You | Forgiveness
SoymL3XAHWk.description:
This gentle Yin Yoga class is going to give you that relaxing deep stretch and relaxation you need. This is a perfect yoga class to do after a long day at work or a stressful week. By using different yin yoga postures we will focus on releasing tension and stiffness out of the back and hips. Remember, breathing is a very important factor in Yin Yoga so through out this entire practice make sure you're taking deep breaths in and long slow exhales out. This yin yoga class is great for beginners or anyone that is looking for something very gentle on the body.  You can even do this yoga class in bed if you like. 
 
Dedicate this 20 minutes to yourself, because you deserve it! Put your own self care as a priority. Breathe, let go of all the negativity in your life, and welcome new positive and vibrant energy with every new breath. 

What is Yin Yoga?

Yin Yoga is a style of yoga practice that targets the connective tissues, such as the ligaments, bones, and even the joints of the body that normally are not exercised very much in a more active style of asana practice.

Suitable for almost all levels, Yin Yoga is a perfect complement to the dynamic and muscular (yang) styles of yoga that emphasize internal heat, and the lengthening and contracting of our muscles. Yin Yoga generally targets the connective tissues of the hips, pelvis, and lower spine.

Each posture in Yin Yoga is usually held up to 5 min or so. However, if you're very new to this I recommend you start with the 1 min holds until you feel more confident in your posture. If you're more of an advanced yogi then feel free to pause the video and hold each pose longer. 

Yin Yoga has many amazing benefits but below are some of the key benefits you may begin to feel after a regular yin practice:

-Stillness: calms and balances the mind and body
-Stress and anxiety reduction
-Increased circulation
-Improved flexibility
-Fascial release


Relax, go deep, enjoy xo

Juliana and Mark

TZxzFaSLj_Y.description:
One of the most effective pilates workout videos we have created for both beginners and advanced. Pilates is an incredible way to accomplish real results, weather it's pilates for weight loss, pilates for core strength, or pilates for toning, you can accomplish so much for your body through this circuit of incredibly effective pilates exercises. 

This week the idea we are focussing on in Tools For A New You is 'focus'. What you think about is what you become. And what you focus on regularly is what you will accomplish. So weather its a fitness or yoga goal, or a general better balance of health and wellness, or any type of dream or goal in your life... write it down, set your intention, and every day ask yourself what you can do to focus on one more small baby step to get you where you need to be. Each day is an inch in the journey, and in time the inches get easier, and eventually turn into feet and then miles. It won't be easy, but commit to the idea, write it down, and every day remind yourself again and again. Before you know it the results will give you momentum. And with momentum it begins to come with ease. And eventually you will be where you want to be.
